<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{فَإِلَهُكُمْ إِلَهٌ وَاحِدٌ فَلَهُ أَسْلِمُوا وَبَشِّرِ الْمُخْبِتِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الحج: ٣٤]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ:</span> <span class="c3">{المُخْبِتِينَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«المُطْمَئِنِّينَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>